                think or feel in that situation).
              </li>
              <li>
                You rate how well each one describes you on a scale from 1 (Not
                Like Me) to 5 (Very Much Like Me).
              </li>
              <li>Each statement corresponds to one of the Big Five traits.</li>
            </ul>
